ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2003-2004
PrecisAppointment of JUDI LONGFIELD of Whitby, Ontario, as Chairman of the Canadian Section of the Canada-United States Permanent Joint Board on Defence in the place of the Honourable Jacques Saada; and request that JUDI LONGFIELD, Member of Parliament for the electoral district of Whitby--Ajax, do undertake such travel as may be necessary for the purposes of the above appointment.
